title: The One About Theme Parks
description:
On this week's episode of Sibling Rivalry Bob and Monét talk about theme parks (kind of). They also dive into black films and old Hollywood controversies. Tune in to find out who hates rollercoasters and who self identifies as a Disney Gay!
